text: Fox Reality Channel was an American pay television channel. It was launched on May 24, 2005. It was owned by the Fox Entertainment Group. The channel aired many shows that were originally on the Fox network. The channel also aired reality shows syndicated from other networks, as well as many international shows from the United Kingdom, Australia, and New Zealand.
